snippet.title: Byte The Dust Trailer (Wishlist now! )
snippet.description:
Wishlist : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3190620/Byte_The_Dust/

"Byte The Dust" Now Has A Steam Page! This Is The First Game I've ever made. It Is A Small Platformer Game Inspired by Getting Over It And Jump King. If You Fall In This Game You might Just Go All The Way Back To Start.

Thank You To Everyone That Has Supported Me The Last 2 Months, All The Support Means A Lot To Me And Has Kept Me Going And Given Me Motivation To Learn Game Dev And Make My First Small Indie Game!
